snippet.title: Citizen Simulation & Lifepath I Feature Highlights Ep 11 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
Let's get to know the citizens who will live in your city, what makes them happy, annoyed, and what will get them to flourish!

Citizens are so much more complex than in the first game, find out what has been changed!

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
